content.rendered:
Directed by Harsha Pulipaka

Written by Harsha Pulipaka. Harsha Pulipaka. Harsha Pulipaka. Sandeep Raj

Cast Naresh Agastya (Vihari). Aadarsh Balakrishna. Brahmanandam (Veda Vyas). Shivathmika Rajashekar (Lekha). Swathi Reddy. Samuthirakani. Satish Saripalli (Vihari Father). Divya Sripada. Srividya (Mythri). Uttej. Rahul Vijay (Subhash). Vikas

Language Telugu

Producers Ravali Kalangi. Suneeth Padolkar. Bhuvan Saluru. Akhilesh Vardhan. Usha Reddy Vavveti. Ramesh Veeragandham. Srujan Yarabolu.

Production S Originals. Ticket Factory.
